  "id": "api/forms/MaxLengthValidator",
  "title": "MaxLengthValidator",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/forms\", \"name\": \"@angular/forms\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\", \"name\": \"MaxLengthValidator\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/forms\">@angular/forms</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L454-L535\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/7.2.0-rc.0/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L454-L535\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"maxlengthvalidator\">MaxLengthValidator<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#maxlengthvalidator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">该指令用于为带有 <code><a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a></code> 属性的控件添加最大长度验证器。该指令会提供 <code><a href=\"api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\" class=\"code-anchor\">NG_VALIDATORS</a></code> 多重提供商列表。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A directive that adds max length validation to controls marked with the\n<code><a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a></code> attribute. The directive is provided with the <code><a href=\"api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\" class=\"code-anchor\">NG_VALIDATORS</a></code> multi-provider list.</p>\n\n\n    \n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n  \n    <li><p><a href=\"guide/form-validation\">Form Validation</a></p>\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n  <h2 id=\"ngmodules\">NgModules<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#ngmodules\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul class=\"ngmodule-list\">\n\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box\">ReactiveFormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n  \n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/FormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box\">FormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n  \n</ul>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">选择器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <ul>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a>][<a href=\"api/forms/FormControlName\" class=\"code-anchor\">formControlName</a>]</code></li>\n    \n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a>][formControl]</code></li>\n    \n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a>][<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]</code></li>\n    \n  </ul>\n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <h2 id=\"属性\">属性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#属性\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>属性</th>\n        <th>说明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"maxlength\"></a>\n          <code><span class=\"property-binding\">@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a></span>: string</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p>Tracks changes to the the maximum length bound to this directive.</p>\n\n          \n          \n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  \n  <section class=\"description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n    <h3 id=\"adding-a-maximum-length-validator\" translation-result=\"on\">添加最大长度验证器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#adding-a-maximum-length-validator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3><h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"adding-a-maximum-length-validator\">Adding a maximum length validator<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#adding-a-maximum-length-validator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">下面的例子演示了如何为一个带有 ngModel 绑定的输入框添加最大长度验证器。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following example shows how to add a maximum length validator to an input attached to an\nngModel binding.</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"html\">\n&#x3C;input name=\"firstName\" <a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a> <a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a>=\"25\">\n</code-example>\n\n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"方法\">方法<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#方法\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n    <a id=\"ngOnChanges\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n    <h3 id=\"ngonchanges\">\n      ngOnChanges()\n      \n    <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#ngonchanges\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L500-L513\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/7.2.0-rc.0/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L500-L513\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p>A lifecycle method called when the directive's inputs change. For internal use\nonly.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  \n\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><span class=\"member-name\">ngOnChanges</span>(<a href=\"api/core/QueryList#changes\" class=\"code-anchor\">changes</a>: <a href=\"api/core/SimpleChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">SimpleChanges</a>): void</code-example>\n\n  \n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数\">参数</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code><a href=\"api/core/QueryList#changes\" class=\"code-anchor\">changes</a></code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/core/SimpleChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">SimpleChanges</a></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p>A object of key/value pairs for the set of changed inputs.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h6>\n  <p><code>void</code></p>\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n  \n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n    <a id=\"validate\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n    <h3 id=\"validate\">\n      validate()\n      \n    <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#validate\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L514-L522\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/7.2.0-rc.0/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L514-L522\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p>Method that validates whether the value exceeds\nthe maximum length requirement.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  \n\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><span class=\"member-name\">validate</span>(control: <a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">AbstractControl</a>): <a href=\"api/forms/ValidationErrors\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidationErrors</a> | null</code-example>\n\n  \n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数-1\">参数</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>control</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">AbstractControl</a></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值-1\">返回值</h6>\n  <p><code><a href=\"api/forms/ValidationErrors\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidationErrors</a> | null</code></p>\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n  \n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n    <a id=\"registerOnValidatorChange\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n    <h3 id=\"registeronvalidatorchange\">\n      registerOnValidatorChange()\n      \n    <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#registeronvalidatorchange\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L523-L530\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/7.2.0-rc.0/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L523-L530\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p>Registers a callback function to call when the validator inputs change.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  \n\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><span class=\"member-name\">registerOnValidatorChange</span>(fn: () => void): void</code-example>\n\n  \n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数-2\">参数</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>fn</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>() => void</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p>The callback function</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值-2\">返回值</h6>\n  <p><code>void</code></p>\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n  \n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core/OnChanges\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - api/forms/Validator\n - api/forms/Validators\n - guide/reactive-forms\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/Input\n - api/core/QueryList#changes\n - api/core/SimpleChanges\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/AbstractControl\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#adding-a-maximum-length-validator\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#description\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#maxlengthvalidator\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#ngmodules\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#ngonchanges\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#registeronvalidatorchange\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#see-also\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#selectors\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#validate\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#属性\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator#方法\n - api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - api/forms/ValidationErrors\n - guide/form-validation\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L454-L535\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L500-L513\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L514-L522\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L523-L530\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/7.2.0-rc.0/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L454-L535\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/7.2.0-rc.0/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L500-L513\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/7.2.0-rc.0/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L514-L522\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/7.2.0-rc.0/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L523-L530\n-->"
